just_use messages.go

# label: WORKHORSE
# role: encodes domain knowledge

Message CRUD + access-filtered listing. Two invariants:

- **All sends are transactional.** SendMessage begins a tx so find-or-
  create-topic + insert-content + FTS-index + insert-message can't
  interleave with a concurrent send on the single DB connection.
- **Edits never overwrite content.** HandleEditMessage inserts a new
  message_content row and re-points messages.content_id at it; the old
  row stays as edit history. Deletes cascade both (content + message)
  in one tx.

Access filter repeats in every SELECT: visible = public channels ∪
user's subscriptions. Factor candidate; currently inlined.
